"                    <code>--primary-color-medium</code> in base.html are hex+alpha composites (the primary color hexwith\n"
"                    an alpha suffix), different from the <code>primary-light</code> / <code>primary-medium</code>values\n"
"                    in <code>tokens.json</code> which are fully opaque mixed colors. Use the opaque mix variantsfor\n"
"                    mobile apps where alpha compositing behaves differently over non-white\n"
"                    backgrounds."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Kumbuka:</strong> <code>--msingi-rangi-mwanga</code> na\n"
"                    <code>--primary-color-medium</code> katika base.html ni composites za hex+alpha (rangi msingi ya hexwith\n"
"                    kiambishi tamati cha alpha), tofauti na thamani za <code>mwangaza-msingi</code> / <code>msingi-kati</code>\n"
"                    katika <code>tokens.json</code> ambazo ni rangi mchanganyiko zisizo wazi. Tumia lahaja za mchanganyiko opaque\n"
"                    programu za simu ambapo utungaji wa alpha hufanya kazi tofauti na zisizo nyeupe\n"
